VF-ST009: case statement requires default branch
Phase: syntax
Location: line 9, column 5
Found: 'end'
Expected: "default =>" before "end case"
Hint:
Every `case` statement must include a `default` branch before `end case`.

Example:
    case choice is
        when 1 =>
            check true
        default =>
            check false = false
    end case
